<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>RPing Spellcasters Guild</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois.cgi?Terrek">Terrek</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 12:19 p.m. 1/7/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> RPing Spellcasters Guild<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/datel.gif" width=46 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dateblnk.gif" width=100 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dater.gif" width=306 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#F4D99F FACE=arial>
<P>Hail and well met children of the good mother!

<P>I scribe this scroll this day so that those who frequent this tavern might join us in our cause. What is our cause you might ask as your read this missive.
<BR>Our cause is twofold friends. First, we wish to help bring to the lands of Norrath the sense that we all play out the roles that we were destined to play from the moment the great wyrm created life on this world. All too many seek the fastest path to power and fame, we would rather take the lesser path, that which leads us all over Norrath such that we might learn of our brothers and sisters in far off realms. Secondly my friends, we wish to provide for a better world for all those that align themselves with the forces of light. By reducing the hold of the greedy, by direct confrontation with the forces of the evil gods and their mindless minions[sp], and by showing a touch of compassion toward those who have met poorly with these evils.
<P>The Order of Ascension is open to all spellcasters who align themselves with the forces of good and wish to play out the roles set before us. Should you have interest, point your magical viewing device to the scroll indicated by the mystic runes below. There upon lies our charter and the bylaws of the Order. Should your interest continue, there are runes at the bottom of that scroll which will allow you to send a missive to me.
<P>May your cause be just and your deaths justified,
<P>Terrek Clouddancer
<BR>Practicioner of the shamanic arts
<BR>Son of Halas
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
<P ALIGN=CENTER><EM><A HREF="http://www.inficad.com/~blifneb/ooa" TARGET=_top>Order of Ascension</A></EM></P>
